# Code Owners
#
# NOTE: owner rules are disabled on purpose. As a solo maintainer, the
# repository owner already receives all activity by default, and active
# CODEOWNERS rules trigger a redundant `review_requested` notification
# (and email) on every single PR, including Dependabot bumps.
#
# To re-enable required reviews (e.g. when a second maintainer joins),
# uncomment the relevant rules and set `require_code_owner_reviews` on
# the branch protection rules.

# Default owners for everything in the repo.
# *                    @elruleh

